name: r-tm
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.7-8" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-tm
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/tm_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/tm/tm_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b1eb1683d956db1a207b61cc086ae08b3ca7f46b6b8bc46d09ba5a4fafa66256

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}            # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}      # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-bh
    - r-nlp >=0.2_0
    - r-rcpp
    - r-slam >=0.1_37
    - r-xml2
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-bh
    - r-nlp >=0.2_0
    - r-rcpp
    - r-slam >=0.1_37
    - r-xml2

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('tm')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('tm')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://tm.r-forge.r-project.org/
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  summary: A framework for text mining applications within R.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
